tip.text: Food was out of this world, cultural blend. We are utterly impressed by this place. chef nelly came out to have a chat, plus we had a candle on my partners dessert. A night we will remember for life.
Love the salmon caviar dish, and not a caprese. Best thing that happened to the north shore.
We were disappointed with the fish (mullet was too tough to be eaten) and the sardines were too fishy. We got the degustation and in hindsight probably better to have preferred individual dishes
We loved the duck dish! Amazing decor- loved this place.
Sensational meal. Great service. Guinea fowl and pasta was amazing.
We arrived after a very long drive from Venice and we were pleased to hear that we were given the best room this place has to offer. Fabulous staff, highly recommended, what a treat!!
A beautiful experience. Truffled guinea fowl was amazing and my pasta was out of this world. Fabulous service and a romantic restaurant! Thank you!
